🚀 Let’s wrap up Black History Month the right way!

We’re bringing together Black-led nonprofits and small businesses for an evening of real connections, meaningful conversations, and community building. Whether you’re looking to collaborate, learn, or just vibe with like-minded changemakers, this is the place to be!

🗓 Friday, February 28, 2025
⏰ 6 PM - 8 PM
📍 Collab Dance Studio & Creative Space
🏢 441 E. Carson St, Carson, CA 90745

It’s all about celebrating our impact, sharing resources, and uplifting each other. Don’t miss out!

🎟 FREE RSVP → www.collabcarson.com/events

Tag a fellow business owner, nonprofit leader, or entrepreneur who should be in the room! Let’s make this a night to remember. ✨💼 #BlackHistoryMonth #StrongerTogether #BlackOwned #CommunityMatters #NetworkingWithPurpose
